    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/5",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\" class=\"has-continuation\">A central thread in his scientific career is the \"ardent pursuit of the concept of roughness\" which resulted in a rich theoretical apparatusâ€”fractal and multifractal geometryâ€”whose aim is to describe and represent the order hidden in apparently wildly</p>",
      "page": 284,
      "polygon": [
        [
          75.734375,
          589.2109375
        ],
        [
          287.0390625,
          589.2109375
        ],
        [
          287.0390625,
          644.7650146484375
        ],
        [
          75.734375,
          644.7650146484375
