    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/7",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">The roughness of clusters in the physics of disorder, of turbulent flows, of exotic noises, of chaotic dynamical systems, of the distribution of galaxies, of coastlines, of stock price charts, and of mathematical constructions,â€”these have typified the topics I studied.</p>",
      "page": 284,
      "polygon": [
        [
          314.7890625,
          113.854736328125
        ],
        [
          503.2578125,
          113.854736328125
