    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/8",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">He formalized the notion of 'fractal process'â€”and later, that of multifractal [13]â€”which provided a tool for quantifying the \"degree of irregularity\" of various random phenomena in mathematics, physics, and economics.</p>",
      "page": 284,
      "polygon": [
