    },
    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/8",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">activity, is given by a multifractal (<i>see</i> <b>Multifractals</b>) increasing process (<i>see</i> <b>Mixture of Distribution</b> <b>Hypothesis</b>; <b>Time Change</b>) [5, 15]:</p>",
      "page": 369,
      "polygon": [
        [
          306.8393249511719,
          71.7884521484375
